            <lg xml:id="TK1170">
<l>uḷḷampōṉ ṟuḷvaḻic celkiṟpiṉ veḷḷanīr</l>
<l> nīntala maṉṉōveṉ kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Could mine eyes travel like my thoughts to the abode (of my absent lord), they would not swim in this flood of tears.</l>
            </lg>
